ion 2.0,=E2=80=9D Anatole Chief Investment Officer George Yang told attende=
es.=C2=A0
Evolution of Fast Fashion
Chief among the new breed of online players from China is Shein. The real-t=
ime retail model that Shein pioneered cuts the time from design to producti=
on from three weeks to as little as three days (although typical times are =
5-7 days). Shein cuts out any of the remaining middlemen, and has built an =
advanced cross-border version of the Consumer to Manufacturer (C2M) model t=
hat Pinduoduo [https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxVkMGOhCAQRL9muI0BAYEDh73=
sb5gWWoesgkHYjX-_OB42mzSQ0KlU1XNQcEn5tHs6CrmusZw72og_x4qlYCb1wDwGb9nQay6FId=
