PiN-UwRyWpfpezHg388-s82peaIuTvqdBRwX51LW_vdrxOir6nNE6J_Nn1pMdb1fIbY-uVW0pNg=
e9ozKplivRw47VgHQgGCMwoU1zArYE4aKsysuZo9nR-Cbkv_z5BkG1OZUg5xaeuvF2y4vhet_Nj=
ercZQzhEjTCv6m0u58b5JjQu2EleiEcoF9UrDzKCouTk0cHwQmjdqpDn71FTxz_QXQKyTDg] pi=
oneered. It plugs directly into competitors=E2=80=99 websites and Google Tr=
end Finder to understand what=E2=80=99s in-fashion, designs quickly, and li=
nks in-app and on-site user behavior to the backend to automatically foreca=
st demand and adjust inventory in real-time, aggressively pushing ads throu=
gh its paid acquisition and influencer referral machine the whole time.=C2=
=A0
We=E2=80=99ll dig more deeply into Shein=E2=80=99s magical machine in a lit=
tle bit, but for now, know that:
It can produce a wider variety of relevant products more cheaply and quickl=
y than competitors (although delivery times are currently still an issue).
It=E2=80=99s working.=C2=A0
