While some of Shein=E2=80=99s relative outperformance can be attributed to =
COVID, there=E2=80=99s a clear shift underway. Shein is picking up steam wh=
ile the OG fast fashion brands slow. Using site traffic and app ranking dat=
a as a proxy to track the health of Shein=E2=80=99s business so far in 2021=
, we can be fairly confident its growth hasn=E2=80=99t slowed as the world =
