rends, and gets pieces from drawing board to store floor in three weeks. Co=
mpared to traditional retail, fast fashion was a revelation. With the adven=
t of fast fashion, a regular person could wear the latest trends and turn o=
ver their wardrobe as frequently as a celebrity, without breaking the bank.=
 Zara pioneered the trend, and while it has an online presence, the company=
 is defined by its retail footprint of nearly 3,000 stores.</p><p style=3D"=
color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">Whi=
