h rates of 19% and 44% growth. ASOS&#8217; market cap is $7 billion, and Bo=
ohoo&#8217;s is $5.7 billion.&nbsp;</p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-siz=
e: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">Yet we now live in the inte=
